summary: Hi Tumblr peeps! I wanted to share with you my first piece for our first show with the @nabiartistcollective! It is titled...
caption:
Hi Tumblr peeps!

I wanted to share with you my first piece for our first show with the @nabiartistcollective!

It is titled “Zephyr” and was painted in gouache and watercolour on watercolour paper.

Our first ever show is along  the “Metamorphosis” theme, and is running from the 1st of June to the 30th of June. Each of us artists will also be auctioning off our pieces during our Facebook auction, from the 5th to the 12th. 
So make sure to follow our Facebook page https://www.facebook.com/Nabi-Artist-Collective-189452301678111/ if you want to get in on the action, and check out all of the other wonderful artists’ work!

Hope to see you there ^^

caption:
Got really pissed @ myself for not drawing anything of substance in May, so now I’m gonna draw daily for June. The theme is Magical Girls, and this first one here is called Princess Cherry! She’s the hero of Harajuku, and she’s a trans lesbian, cuz it is pride after all.

If you like her, she is up for adoption! $45 bucks, first come first served. (catch me at my gmail: indirarmedeiros@gmail.com)
